{
  "texts": [
    "We assess and respond to the manipulation objection in the next section.",
    "Consider the following example.",
    "A disinformation campaign uses purposefully biased AI polls to inject spurious preferences in a national political discourse, at a granular level.",
    "Like many AI polls, they claim their model is a 'black box', and cannot be easily audited.",
    "They release the underlying data, but it is impossible to ascertain what adjustments were made to the data by the AI, due to its black-box nature."
  ]
}